         ("The Honest Take", "<p>Kelley is the higher-ranked, more broadly recognized program. If admitted to both, Kelley is the default choice for most careers. Gies makes sense for candidates who value UIUC's tech ecosystem, who receive significantly better financial aid, or who want to stay in the Champaign-Chicago corridor. For operations and supply chain, Kelley is unbeatable.</p>"),
